Class ImageFilterRasterDataSource

All Implemented Interfaces:
RasterDataSource
public class ImageFilterRasterDataSource
extends AbstractRasterDataSource

Data source for processing (filtering) source tile images. This can be used to perform simple image manipulations (contrast enhancement, for example) on source tiles.
